title: wfdebug - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: usage: wfdebug <pattern matching expression for workflow names> ... <ON|OFF> This command is used to enable or disable debug information for a workflow. Note that turning on the Debug mode might slow down the workflow due to log filing. Return Codes Listed below are the different return codes for the unregister command: Code Description Code Description 0 Will be returned if the command was successful. 1 Will be returned if the argument count is incorrect.
